Package: OrchidGermClass
Title: Orchid Class Germination Predictor
Version: 1.0.0.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("Spyridon", "Oikonomidis", , "soikonomidis@biol.uoa.gr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The purpose of the present package is to offer an initial screening tool of orchid germination behaviour by classifying orchid species in germination classes based on their seed morphological data and supplemented by taxnomic and ecological niche data for each taxon
